{
  "id": "2CO.2",
  "bibleId": "de4e12af7f28f599-01",
  "number": "2",
  "bookId": "2CO",
  "reference": "2 Corinthians 2",
  "copyright": "PUBLIC DOMAIN except in the United Kingdom, where a Crown Copyright applies to printing the KJV. See http://www.cambridge.org/about-us/who-we-are/queens-printers-patent",
  "verseCount": 17,
  "content": [
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "1",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "But I determined this with myself, that I would not come again to you in heaviness. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "2",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:2"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "2",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For if I make you sorry, who is he then that maketh me glad, but the same which is made sorry by me? ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.2",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "3",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:3"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And I wrote this same unto you, lest, when I came, I should have sorrow from them of whom I ought to rejoice; having confidence in you all, that my joy is ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "the joy",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.3",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.3"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " of you all. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "4",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:4"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "4",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For out of much affliction and anguish of heart I wrote unto you with many tears; not that ye should be grieved, but that ye might know the love which I have more abundantly unto you. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "5",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:5"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "5",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "But if any have caused grief, he hath not grieved me, but in part: that I may not overcharge you all. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.5",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "6",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:6"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "6",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Sufficient to such a man ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.6",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.6"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " this punishment, which ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "was inflicted",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.6",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.6"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " of many. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "7",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:7"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "7",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "So that contrariwise ye ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "ought",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.7"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " rather to forgive ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "him",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.7"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ", and comfort ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "him",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.7"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ", lest perhaps such a one should be swallowed up with overmuch sorrow. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "8",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:8"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "8",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Wherefore I beseech you that ye would confirm ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "your",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.8",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.8"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " love toward him. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "9",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:9"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "9",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For to this end also did I write, that I might know the proof of you, whether ye be obedient in all things. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "10",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:10"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "10",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "To whom ye forgive any thing, I ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "forgive",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " also: for if I forgave any thing, to whom I forgave ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "it",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ", for your sakes ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "forgave I it",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " in the person of Christ; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "11",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:11"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "11",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Lest Satan should get an advantage of us: for we are not ignorant of his devices. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "12",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:12"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "12",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Furthermore, when I came to Troas to ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "preach",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.12",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.12"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " Christ’s gospel, and a door was opened unto me of the Lord, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "13",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:13"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "13",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "I had no rest in my spirit, because I found not Titus my brother: but taking my leave of them, I went from thence into Macedonia. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.13",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.13"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "14",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:14"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "14",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Now thanks ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "be",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.14",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.14"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " unto God, which always causeth us to triumph in Christ, and maketh manifest the savour of his knowledge by us in every place. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "15",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:15"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "15",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For we are unto God a sweet savour of Christ, in them that are saved, and in them that perish: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.15",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "16",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:16"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "16",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "To the one ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "we are",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.16",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.16"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " the savour of death unto death; and to the other the savour of life unto life. And who ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "2CO.2.16",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "2CO.2.16"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " sufficient for these things? ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "17",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "2CO 2:17"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "17",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For we are not as many, which corrupt the word of God: but as of sincerity, but as of God, in the sight of God speak we in Christ.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "2CO.2.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "2CO.2.17"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
